# Exclude PDF build artifacts from Quarto project scanning.
# These .tex files are generated by 'keep-tex: true' in PDF configs
# (needed for .lof figure manifest generation) and land in the project root.
# Without this file, a Vol1 HTML build picks up Vol2 .tex cross-references,
# producing spurious "Unable to resolve crossref" warnings.
*.tex

# Exclude volume-specific index files from auto-discovery.
# HTML builds create an index.qmd symlink pointing to the active volume's
# landing page (e.g. index-vol1.qmd). Without this exclusion, Quarto
# discovers both the symlink AND the real file, renders both to index.html,
# and crashes on the rename collision (safeMoveSync ENOENT).
# PDF/EPUB builds use type:book which doesn't auto-discover, so this is
# only load-bearing for HTML website builds.
index-vol1.qmd
index-vol2.qmd
